name: CoreAPI Security_User
description: API to access results of Planet 9 Security_User Details.
about:
Description

Planet 9-Security_User facilitates to add the new user and maintain them to access Planet 9.

You can use API Security_User in your app if you want to add, delete, and update the user. 

API Security_User is the Planet 9 API to access the  Planet 9 Users and the operations performed on them. Also, you can assign the defined "Roles" to the user from the app using Security_User API. (Roles could be created from API Security_Roles)

Every app must have the right roles (permissions) and authentication that enables access to the Security_User API.
